<p>The following appointments are made to the aforesaid Companiesof Sergeants and Corporals;<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-03-02-0238-fn-0008" id="GEWN-02-03-02-0238-fn-0008-ptr">8</a> who are not to be broke or changed, but by the Sentence of a Court Martialor particular orders from the Colonel: as such practices have made great confusion in the Regiments. vizt</p>
